l=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0~n79uu-5b6sn.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/16wgh3p.el.sw.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/03iwt00g3c5jb.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0vsxbp8eomjbt.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0v9sk1_dwm88i.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0-040446ad9-w.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0~e4pb9i85b~b.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/1306_f_4~kby~.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0058_u3~h-~eq.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0ij27du5soce0.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0.mdjjajlylgt.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0qxqchq04f22x.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0t_n-ooo~x1km.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/05pxzoikotag4.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/11qg728ocz1h0.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0erkiz588n9f6.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0nr7pxhbvjz8m.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/112r.w_sm1tf..js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0tsa6v~u~.dtb.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/0~rw~ww~yfj3d.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\",\"/_next/static/chunks/169hdo-~qf8gp.js?dpl=a-27723880215-1-c18dc4c134775f20\"],\"default\"]\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4d:T170a,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a photography portfolio that looks professional and you don't need design skills to make it work. The finished portfolio looks custom-built, not template-based—important when you're competing against photographers with established businesses and bigger budgets. Show your best projects in full-screen galleries, organize work by category, and let potential clients contact you directly through a built-in form.\n\nThe technical parts are already handled. Mobile responsiveness, image galleries with simple navigation, dark mode switching, and contact form validation—all working out of the box. You can focus on uploading your best work and writing descriptions that connect with the clients you want to attract.\n\nYour images are the focus. The template uses full-screen viewing with smooth fade transitions between photos, clean layouts, and minimal interface elements that keep attention on your photography rather than the UI.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Photographers launching independent businesses who need portfolios that look custom-built, not template-based, to compete against established studios with bigger budgets\n\n- Photography service businesses that need professional online presence to justify premium pricing without hiring developers or designers\n\n- Creative professionals who want to prove their business concept works through a polished portfolio that clients take seriously\n\n- Photographers in specialized fields—real estate, portraits, events, product photography—who need to differentiate from competitors using basic website builders\n\n- Creative agencies showcasing photography services alongside other offerings like design or videography\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n### Project-Based Photography Portfolios\n\nOrganize your work into distinct projects with multiple images per shoot. Show editorial spreads, commercial campaigns, or personal series with dedicated pages for each project. The template handles multiple images smoothly, and clients can view full-screen galleries with simple navigation. This works well when you need to show depth and range within specific photography categories.\n\n### Category-Organized Showcases\n\nSort your photography into categories like portraits, landscapes, editorial, architecture, or documentary work. Potential clients can browse your work organized by type—portraits, landscapes, editorial, architecture, or documentary. This organization helps when you work across multiple photography styles—clients can navigate directly to the category that matches their needs.\n\n### Client Acquisition Tools\n\nUse the portfolio to attract new photography clients with a professional contact form and clear presentation. The about page lets you explain your approach and experience, while project pages demonstrate the quality clients can expect. The professional appearance helps justify premium rates and compete with established photographers—without looking like you used a template.\n\n### Transition from Hobby to Business\n\nBuild credibility as you move from hobby photography to paid work. The portfolio gives you a professional web presence that looks custom-built rather than template-based. This matters when you're competing for early clients against photographers with established businesses. The site grows with you—add projects as you complete them, update your about page as you gain experience, and refine categories as your focus becomes clearer.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete photography portfolio ready to customize. All the pages and features are already working—you just need to make it yours.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nChange colors to match your photography style. Update fonts to reflect your aesthetic. Lovable's visual editor lets you modify layouts and see changes instantly as you work. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Content\n\nReplace the sample projects with your best photography work. Upload images, write project descriptions that explain your creative approach, and organize shoots into categories that make sense for your business. The template stays out of your way so your photography is what people notice, not the interface.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nThe template is ready to deploy as-is with all core features working. As your business grows, you can add integrations like analytics or booking tools—Lovable's architecture is built to expand when you need it.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nDeploy your photography portfolio with one click. Lovable handles hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Your portfolio goes live worldwide in minutes, and you can start sharing the URL with your audience. The site loads fast, works on all devices, and gives clients a professional first impression of your work.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis photography portfolio template works for photographers who want their site to look as professional as their images. You get custom design without hiring a developer, fast image galleries without technical optimization, and all the features working photographers actually need—project organization, organized categories, client contact forms, and mobile-responsive layouts. The professional presentation helps you compete for clients against photographers with bigger budgets and more established businesses.\n\nWhether you're transitioning from hobby photography to paid work or upgrading from a basic portfolio site, this template gives you a professional foundation. The full-screen galleries work smoothly, organized categories help clients navigate to relevant work, and the contact form makes it easy for potential clients to reach you. Choose this template to launch a photography portfolio that showcases your work professionally and helps you attract the clients you want.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4e:T7a5,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"\nBuild presentations that go beyond static slides. Combine the familiarity of traditional slide decks with the power of code and interactive web components.\n\n## Perfect For\n\n- **Product Demos**: Show live features with interactive components and real-time data\n- **Business Pitches**: Dynamic charts, calculations, and data visualizations\n- **Educational Content**: Interactive learning with simulations and explorable examples\n- **Technical Showcases**: Complex visualizations, 3D graphics, and custom interactions\n- **Conference Talks**: Engaging presentations with live coding examples and demos\n\n## Key Capabilities\n\n**Code-Powered Flexibility** - Build anything you can create with React. Add custom components, interactive charts, data visualizations, forms, animations, or any web technology.\n\n**Real-Time Interactivity** - Create presentations where users can manipulate parameters, adjust values, and see results update live. Perfect for demos and educational content.\n\n**No Limitations** - Unlike PowerPoint or Google Slides, you have complete control. Use any npm package, connect to APIs, or build custom interactions tailored to your needs.\n\n**Professional Delivery** - Beautiful gradients, modern design system, fullscreen presentation mode, and keyboard navigation for polished presentations.\n\n## Technical Features\n\n- Fixed 1920x1080 resolution with automatic scaling\n- Sidebar thumbnail navigation\n- Fullscreen presentation mode with keyboard controls\n- Progress indicators and zoom controls\n- Mobile-responsive layouts\n- Keyboard navigation (arrow keys, Space, Escape)\n\n## Use This Template\n\nStart with 6 pre-built example slides showing what's possible:\n1. Title slide with gradient background\n2. Interactive charts and simulations\n3. Real-time calculations and metrics\n4. 3D object viewer\n5. Custom interactive components\n6. Call-to-action slide\n\nCustomize everything—colors, content, interactions, and components to match your needs.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"4f:T10fe,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you an architecture portfolio with a clear, disciplined structure that doesn’t require design expertise. The neutral, minimal system suits architects, studios, interior designers, and creative teams who need a site that reflects professional standards.\n\nThe technical setup is already handled. Your projects display correctly on all devices, navigation stays orderly, and clients can move through your work without friction. You can focus on selecting projects that represent your capabilities. The monochrome presentation removes visual noise so your work sets the tone.\n\nWhether you’re creating your first independent portfolio or replacing a site that doesn’t reflect your studio’s standards, this template gives you a structure that adapts to your content instead of forcing rigid layouts.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Architecture firms presenting residential, commercial, cultural, or mixed-use work\n- Interior designers developing a professional digital presence\n- Design studios organizing multi-category project work\n- Independent architects establishing credibility during a transition to solo practice\n- Creative agencies preparing work for client pitches\n- Design consultants positioning themselves for higher-value engagements\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n**Project Portfolios**: Give each project its own space with large imagery and clear information such as location, area, year, and category. Visitors can filter by project type to find relevant work immediately. This helps clients evaluate whether your experience aligns with their needs without scanning unrelated examples.\n\n**Client Acquisition**: Your presentation quality shapes early judgments. Prospects reviewing several firms want orderly pages, consistent formatting, and detail that helps them understand your range. Clear navigation, accurate project information, and an uncluttered layout make it easier for qualified leads to reach out through direct contact links.\n\n**Studio Presence**: Build a complete studio identity with pages for your services, process, and team. The built-in blog lets you share updates, project walkthroughs, and design thinking. This helps you communicate your approach instead of relying solely on final images. Dark mode support provides a comfortable viewing option for late-night research.\n\n**Thought Leadership**: Publish project case studies, write-ups, and design insights. The topic filters help visitors move through your thinking without searching manually. Teams that secure work through documented expertise and strong viewpoints benefit from having a space to organize and present that material clearly.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick **Remix** to create your version. Project galleries, filters, the blog, dark mode, and theme controls are already configured. Replace the sample content with your own work.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nAdjust colors, typography, and layout spacing to match your studio identity. The visual editor updates everything in real time. The minimal base gives you a stable starting point without requiring code changes.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Projects\n\nUpload high-quality imagery and add relevant project details. Organize your work by category so the filtering tools work cleanly. Write concise descriptions that communicate your intent, constraints, and results. The structure keeps focus on the work itself.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nAdd your project management links, connect Supabase forms for inquiries, integrate analytics, or attach testimonial platforms. These additions help clients move from browsing to contacting you without extra steps.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nPublish with one click. Hosting, performance, and security are handled automatically. Share the link in proposals, presentations, email signatures, and social profiles.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis architecture portfolio template gives you a clean structure that supports the way professional firms present their work. Project pages stay organized, imagery displays correctly, and visitors can move through your content without confusion. The filtering system keeps navigation direct, and the design adapts to your content from the first build.\n\nChoose this template to create a portfolio that reflects your standards, supports client decisions, and grows alongside your practice.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"50:Tcc4,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a fashion blog that looks professional and you don't need design skills to make it work.\n\nThe technical parts are already handled. Mobile responsiveness, fast loading, SEO setup—all done. You can focus on creating content your readers want to see.\n\n## **Who This Is For**\n\n- Fashion bloggers building their personal brand and online presence\n- Style influencers who need professional layouts for outfit posts and lookbooks\n- Personal stylists showcasing their work and attracting new clients\n- Boutique owners combining blog content with product features\n- Lifestyle creators covering fashion, beauty, and trends\n\n## **Best Use Cases**\n\n**Personal Style Blogs**: Document your daily outfits, seasonal wardrobes, and fashion experiments. The layouts work well for visual storytelling, which is what personal style content needs.\n\n**Fashion Reviews**: Review clothing brands, test sustainable fashion, and share honest product opinions. Readers who trust your taste will come back for your recommendations.\n\n**Trend Analysis**: Cover runway shows, street style, and emerging trends. The professional layouts help establish you as someone who knows what they're talking about in the industry.\n\n**Styling Services**: Show before-and-after transformations and share client success stories. The portfolio-quality presentation helps you attract new styling clients who want to see proof of your work.\n\n## **Getting Started**\n\n**Step 1: Remix This Template**\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete fashion blog ready to customize. All the pages and features are already working—you just need to make it yours.\n\n**Step 2: Customize Your Brand**\n\nChange colors to match your aesthetic. Update fonts to reflect your style. Lovable's visual editor lets you modify layouts and see changes instantly as you work. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n**Step 3: Add Your Content**\n\nReplace the sample posts with your outfit photos, styling tips, and fashion commentary. Upload your best images and write captions that connect with your audience. The template stays out of your way so your content is what people notice.\n\n**Step 4: Connect Your Tools**\n\nLink your Instagram feed, connect email marketing through Supabase, add Google Analytics, or integrate affiliate platforms. Lovable has built-in integrations for the tools fashion bloggers actually use.\n\n**Step 5: Go Live**\n\nDeploy your fashion blog with one click. Lovable handles the hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Your blog goes live worldwide in minutes, and you can start sharing the URL with your audience.\n\n## **Conclusion**\n\nThis fashion blog template works for creators who want their site to look as polished as their content. You get professional design without hiring a developer, fast performance without technical optimization, and all the features fashion bloggers actually use. Whether you're starting your first blog or upgrading from a basic platform, this template gives you a solid foundation. The image galleries work properly, mobile navigation is smooth, and everything loads fast from day one. Choose this template to launch a fashion blog that represents your style and grows with your audience.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"51:T9e8,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a professional event platform that works without technical setup. Registration forms, event listings, and mobile-ready layouts are already built. You focus on organizing events and getting people in the room—the infrastructure is handled.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Event organizers running conferences, workshops, or community gatherings\n- Community builders hosting recurring meetups\n- Conference teams needing registration and attendee management\n- Workshop facilitators selling tickets and managing enrollments\n- Corporate teams running internal events or training sessions\n- Creators hosting webinars or virtual sessions\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n**Conference Management**: Run multi-day events with speaker lineups, session schedules, and attendee registration. Participants can browse the agenda and sign up for sessions that interest them.\n\n**Community Meetups**: Host recurring meetups without rebuilding registration each time. Members see upcoming events, RSVP, and access all essential details.\n\n**Workshop Sales**: Sell tickets for classes or training sessions. The platform handles registration while you focus on delivering strong content.\n\n**Corporate Events**: Manage internal gatherings, client functions, or training sessions. The clean presentation works across small team events and larger company-wide programs.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick **Remix** to create your copy. Registration, event pages, and attendee flows are already in place.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nAdjust colors, fonts, and layout emphasis. Lovable’s visual editor updates in real time — no coding required.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Events\n\nCreate listings with dates, locations, descriptions, and speaker details. Add registration forms that capture attendee information.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nIntegrate Supabase for attendee data, Stripe for paid tickets, and calendar tools so attendees can save event dates. These connections take minutes.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nDeploy with one click. Hosting and performance are handled automatically, so your platform is ready as soon as you publish.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis event platform template works for organizers who need reliable event infrastructure without building from scratch. You get professional presentation, working registration flows, and a platform that handles logistics cleanly. Use it to launch event series, manage workshops, or centralize conference operations—everything displays clearly and works on every device.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"52:Td1a,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a newsletter site that looks professional and you don't need design skills to make it work.\n\nThe technical parts are already handled. Mobile responsiveness, fast loading, email signup forms—all done. You can focus on creating content your readers want to see.\n\n## **Who This Is For**\n\n- Writers and journalists building independent publications\n- Industry experts sharing insights and analysis with their audience\n- Creators monetizing through paid subscriptions and sponsorships\n- Thought leaders establishing authority in their field\n- Companies and brands running content marketing newsletters\n- Podcasters and video creators adding written content to their offering\n\n## **Best Use Cases**\n\n**Independent Publishing**: Launch your own publication without platform fees eating into your revenue. You own the subscriber list and control how you monetize your writing.\n\n**Industry Commentary**: Share weekly or monthly analysis about your industry. The clean layout keeps readers focused on your insights instead of fighting with cluttered design.\n\n**Curated Digests**: Compile the best articles, resources, and links in your niche. Readers subscribe because you save them time finding what matters, and the template makes curation look effortless.\n\n**Personal Thought Leadership**: Build your reputation by consistently sharing valuable perspectives. The professional presentation signals credibility before readers even start reading your content.\n\n## **Getting Started**\n\n**Step 1: Remix This Template**\n\nClick \"Remix\" to create your copy. You'll have a complete newsletter site ready to customize. All the pages and features are already working—you just need to make it yours.\n\n**Step 2: Customize Your Brand**\n\nChange colors to match your aesthetic. Update fonts to reflect your style. Lovable's visual editor lets you modify layouts and see changes instantly as you work. You don't need to know code to make it look exactly how you want.\n\n**Step 3: Add Your Content**\n\nReplace the sample issues with your writing, analysis, and commentary. Upload your author photo and write a bio that connects with your target audience. The template stays out of your way so your content is what people notice.\n\n**Step 4: Connect Your Tools**\n\nIntegrate email service providers like Supabase for subscriber management, connect Stripe for paid subscriptions, or add analytics to track which topics resonate. Lovable has built-in integrations for the tools newsletter publishers actually use.\n\n**Step 5: Go Live**\n\nDeploy your newsletter site with one click. Lovable handles the hosting, security, and performance optimization automatically. Your publication goes live worldwide in minutes, and you can start building your subscriber list.\n\n## **Conclusion**\n\nThis newsletter template works for creators who want their publication to look as polished as their writing. You get professional design without hiring a developer and fast performance without technical optimization. Whether you're starting your first newsletter or moving from a platform that takes a cut of your revenue, this template gives you a solid foundation. The signup forms work properly, mobile reading experience is smooth, and everything loads fast from day one. Choose this template to launch a newsletter that represents your voice and grows with your audience.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"53:Tf2e,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a complete lifestyle blog with clean presentation and no technical setup. Masonry grids support mixed content. Featured article sections highlight your strongest posts. Organized category pages help readers move through your ideas without friction.\n\nMobile performance, fast image handling, search, category filtering, and basic SEO configuration are already in place. You can publish immediately instead of troubleshooting formatting or structure. The design keeps attention on your writing rather than on template mechanics.\n\nThis works for personal branding, subject matter publishing, or client content builds. You get a foundation that reads professionally and scales with your output.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Solopreneurs shaping a consistent presence in their field\n- Small business owners using content to attract and educate potential clients\n- Consultants and service providers demonstrating expertise for decision makers\n- Agencies delivering client blogs without development cycles\n- Content creators in lifestyle, wellness, fashion, tech, business, or culture\n- Marketing teams that need a functioning content system without engineering delays\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n**Personal Brand Publishing**: Share expertise, document progress, and establish a recognizable voice. The layouts present your work cleanly so readers can evaluate your perspective quickly. This helps create recognition and makes your content easier to recommend.\n\n**Service Business Content**: Show prospects you understand their needs through targeted articles. The category structure and filtering help readers locate content that matches their situation. Strong content creates trust before an initial conversation.\n\n**Agency Client Workflows**: Build client blogs without custom coding or long timelines. You can present functioning prototypes during pitches and deliver final sites without engineering support. This helps agencies maintain margins while expanding deliverable types.\n\n**Multi Topic Platforms**: Publish across several categories without confusing readers. Category pages and filtering separate topics cleanly so different audience segments can find what matters to them. The design handles varied subject matter without visual clutter.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick Remix to create your copy. Homepage layouts, article templates, categories, search, and contact forms are already working.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nAdjust colors and typography to match your visual identity. The editor updates layouts in real time so your changes are easy to evaluate. You can refine navigation, grid spacing, and featured sections without touching code.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Content\n\nReplace the sample posts with your writing. Upload images and organize articles into logical categories. The layout keeps focus on your ideas. Filtering and search adapt automatically to your structure.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nAdd analytics to monitor reader behavior, connect your email platform, integrate social profiles, or attach affiliate systems. Newsletter forms and share components are already in place. You only need to attach your service credentials.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nPublish with one click. Hosting, security, and performance tuning are handled for you. Your blog loads quickly on phones and desktops, and you can share the URL across platforms immediately.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis lifestyle blog template gives you a clean publishing system with the features content creators rely on. You get organized categories, functional search, fast loading, and layouts that give your work room to breathe. It supports personal brands, client projects, and multi topic content plans.\n\nChoose this template to publish consistently, present your ideas clearly, and maintain a professional digital presence without added technical overhead.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"54:Tde7,"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"This template gives you a complete e-commerce store that looks polished without requiring design skills or technical setup. Product pages, checkout flows, mobile layouts, and cart functionality are already in place.\n\nEverything works on every device. Customers can browse, zoom in on details, add items to their cart, and check out smoothly without you configuring layouts or handling complex storefront logic. Your focus stays on adding products and preparing for sales instead of troubleshooting an online store.\n\nThe minimalist luxury presentation avoids the generic appearance common in off-the-shelf builders. The layouts keep attention on your products and support premium positioning.\n\n## Who This Is For\n\n- Solopreneurs launching product lines and testing demand without developer expense\n\n- Small business owners needing a professional store that supports higher price points\n\n- Agencies delivering client storefronts on tight timelines without draining project resources\n\n- Product sellers exploring new distribution channels or direct-to-consumer sales\n\n- Entrepreneurs creating lifestyle brands who need a storefront that elevates product perception\n\n## Best Use Cases\n\n**Luxury Product Retail**: Sell premium goods with presentation that strengthens perceived quality. Customers see detail and craftsmanship clearly, which reinforces the value of higher-end items.\n\n**Multi-Category Stores**: Organize products across clean, intuitive categories so shoppers can move through your catalog quickly. Finding specific items feels simple, even with larger inventories.\n\n**Artisan and Maker Shops**: Showcase handcrafted work with space for brand storytelling. The template supports pages for your origin story, sustainability notes, care instructions, and store locations. This structure helps customers connect with the value behind your products.\n\n**Direct-to-Consumer Launches**: Launch fast and validate demand immediately. Highlight key products, surface recommendations that lift order values, and start processing real orders without a long development cycle.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n### Step 1: Remix This Template\n\nClick Remix to create your version. All pages and core commerce features are active the moment your copy is generated.\n\n### Step 2: Customize Your Brand\n\nAdjust colors, typography, and layout details through the visual editor. Changes appear instantly, and you never need to handle code. Your store looks aligned with your brand from the start.\n\n### Step 3: Add Your Products\n\nUpload your catalog, add high-quality images, and write clear product descriptions. The layout keeps attention on your products instead of the interface.\n\n### Step 4: Connect Your Tools\n\nAdd your payment provider, set up order notifications, and connect any supporting tools you use. Stripe and other standard integrations work out of the box.\n\n### Step 5: Go Live\n\nDeploy your store with one click. Hosting, performance, and security are handled for you so you can start sharing your store and serving customers immediately.\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThis e-commerce template is shaped for product sellers who want a clean, credible storefront without technical barriers. The structure supports premium branding, the checkout flow is ready from the moment you remix, and the browsing experience stays fast and consistent on every device. It lets you focus on products, customers, and early sales while the platform handles the rest.\n\nChoose this template to launch a store that reflects your brand quality and converts first-time browsers into paying customers.\n"])</script><script nonce="F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==">self.__next_f.push([1,"25:[[\"$\",\"script\",null,{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"nonce\":\"F8nTuJg2/dJTEd/Tu8dvvw==\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Lovable\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://lovable.dev\\\",\\\"logo\\\":\\\"https://lovable.dev/favicon-192x192.png\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Lovable is your superhuman full stack engineer. Chat with AI to build web apps. Sync with GitHub. One-click deploy.\\\",\\\"sameAs\\\":[\\\"https://twitter.com/lovable\\\",\\\"https://www.linkedin.com/company/lovable-dev\\\",\\\"https://www.youtube.com/@lovable\\\",\\\"https://github.com/lovablelabs\\\"],\\\"foundingDate\\\":\\\"2023\\\",\\\"contactPoint\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"ContactPoint\\\",\\\"contactType\\\":\\\"Customer Support\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://lovable.dev/support\\\"}}\"}}],[\"$\",\"$L4c\",null,{\"templates\":[{\"slug\":\"hobby-photographer\",\"id\":\"hobby-photographer-portfolio\",\"title\":\"Personal portfolio\",\"pageTitle\":\"Hobby Photographer - Photography Portfolio Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"96ce7324-2bfa-401f-a87d-7eb158e7b479\",\"url\":\"https://hobby-photographer-template.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Launch a professional photography portfolio that attracts paying clients. Full-screen galleries, category organization, and contact forms—ready to deploy in hours, not weeks.\",\"tagline\":\"Personal work showcase\",\"description\":\"Launch a professional photography portfolio that attracts paying clients. Full-screen galleries, category organization, and contact forms—ready to deploy in hours, not weeks.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Photography Portfolio Template | Showcase Your Work | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Launch a beautiful photography portfolio that showcases your work professionally. Full-screen galleries, contact forms, and mobile-ready design - no coding required.\",\"subcategory\":\"portfolio\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Portfolio\",\"Photography\",\"Hobby\",\"Personal\",\"Amateur\",\"Casual\"],\"screenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/hobby-photographer-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/hobby-photographer-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/previews/hobby-photographer-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#FFFFFF\",\"#2C2C2C\",\"#F0F0F0\",\"#E0E0E0\",\"#444444\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2025-11-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"lastModified\":\"2025-11-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"image_stack\",\"title\":\"Professional Image Showcase System\",\"description\":\"Full-screen lightbox galleries with keyboard navigation designed for photographers presenting client work professionally\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance Optimized\",\"description\":\"Sub-2 second load times with lazy loading, code splitting, and optimized images for immediate visual impact\"},{\"icon\":\"devices\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Pixel-perfect layouts across all devices ensuring your photography looks stunning on every screen size\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Dark Mode With System Detection\",\"description\":\"Automatic theme switching respects visitor preferences while maintaining professional aesthetic across both modes\"},{\"icon\":\"check_circle\",\"title\":\"Zero Technical Maintenance Required\",\"description\":\"Static architecture with optimized assets means no server management, updates, or technical overhead costs\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Interactive Lightbox Gallery\",\"description\":\"Full-screen image viewing with touch gestures, keyboard navigation, and smooth fade transitions for professional portfolio presentations that keep visitors engaged\"},{\"title\":\"Interactive Project Previews\",\"description\":\"When visitors hover over your project thumbnails, images smoothly zoom and display project details, creating an engaging browsing experience that showcases your work professionally\"},{\"title\":\"Smart Contact Form\",\"description\":\"Your contact form automatically checks that visitors fill out required fields correctly (like valid email addresses), showing helpful error messages if something's wrong and a confirmation when their message sends successfully\"},{\"title\":\"Smart Navigation Menu\",\"description\":\"Your menu starts transparent over your images and becomes solid as visitors scroll down, keeping it easy to find while looking beautiful at the top of your page\"},{\"title\":\"Swipe Through Photos on Mobile\",\"description\":\"Visitors can naturally swipe left and right to browse your gallery photos on phones and tablets, just like they're used to in their favorite photo apps\"},{\"title\":\"Keyboard-Friendly Navigation\",\"description\":\"Visitors who use keyboards instead of mice (including those with accessibility needs) can easily navigate through your galleries and menus, making your portfolio welcoming to everyone\"}],\"content\":\"$4d\",\"relativePath\":\"hobby-photographer.md\"},{\"slug\":\"lovable-slides\",\"id\":\"f003850e-32d2-409c-8cfc-5fc9e5ea172f\",\"title\":\"Lovable slides\",\"pageTitle\":\"Interactive Presentation Builder Template\",\"category\":\"Apps\",\"project_id\":\"f003850e-32d2-409c-8cfc-5fc9e5ea172f\",\"url\":\"https://lov-slides.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Code-powered presentation builder\",\"description\":\"Create professional presentations with unlimited possibilities. Add interactive charts, real-time calculations, custom components, and anything you can build with React. Perfect for demos, education, and business pitches.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Interactive Presentation Template | Lovable Slides | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Build interactive slide decks with live data, custom components, and dynamic interactions. A modern alternative to static presentations - deploy in minutes.\",\"subcategory\":\"saas\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/lovable-slides-final.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/lovable-slides-final.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/lovable-slides-final.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Aleksander Heino\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2026-12-31T23:59:59.000Z\",\"lastModified\":\"2026-02-12T18:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"code\",\"title\":\"Code-Powered Interactivity\",\"description\":\"Build anything you can imagine with React—interactive charts, simulations, calculators, and custom components that respond to user input\"},{\"icon\":\"sync\",\"title\":\"Live Data and Real-Time Updates\",\"description\":\"Connect to APIs, display dynamic calculations, and show real-time metrics that update as users interact with your slides\"},{\"icon\":\"widgets\",\"title\":\"Beyond Static Slides\",\"description\":\"Embed 3D graphics, interactive visualizations, forms, animations, or any web component directly in your presentation\"},{\"icon\":\"palette\",\"title\":\"Full Customization Control\",\"description\":\"Complete design freedom with React components, CSS styling, and modern web technologies—no template constraints\"},{\"icon\":\"presentation\",\"title\":\"Professional Presentation Mode\",\"description\":\"Fullscreen mode with keyboard navigation, thumbnail sidebar, zoom controls, and smooth transitions for polished delivery\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"React Component Architecture\",\"description\":\"Build slides with React components—create interactive charts, data visualizations, forms, animations, or any custom UI you need for your presentation.\"},{\"title\":\"Real-Time Interactivity\",\"description\":\"Add live calculations, adjustable parameters, and dynamic content that updates as users interact. Perfect for demos, simulations, and educational content.\"},{\"title\":\"Embed Any Web Technology\",\"description\":\"Use 3D libraries, data visualization frameworks, animation libraries, or any npm package. Build presentations as powerful as web applications.\"},{\"title\":\"Fixed Resolution Scaling System\",\"description\":\"All slides render at 1920x1080 and scale perfectly to any screen size using transform scaling, ensuring consistent appearance across all devices and projectors.\"},{\"title\":\"Professional Presentation Controls\",\"description\":\"Fullscreen mode with keyboard navigation (arrow keys), thumbnail sidebar for quick navigation, zoom controls, and progress indicators for smooth delivery.\"},{\"title\":\"Flexible Layout System\",\"description\":\"Responsive grid layouts that adapt from mobile to desktop. Use Tailwind CSS or custom styles to create exactly the layout you need.\"},{\"title\":\"State Management Built In\",\"description\":\"Use React hooks and state to create interactive slides where user actions affect what's displayed. Build multi-step demonstrations and guided experiences.\"},{\"title\":\"Code-First Workflow\",\"description\":\"Edit slides as React components with full TypeScript support. Version control your presentations with git and collaborate like you would on any code project.\"}],\"content\":\"$4e\",\"relativePath\":\"lovable-slides.md\"},{\"slug\":\"architect-portfolio-1\",\"id\":\"architect-portfolio-1\",\"title\":\"Architect Portfolio Website Template\",\"pageTitle\":\"Architect Portfolio Website Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"09a14ae7-bd4a-415b-b22e-66bbeb1a9240\",\"url\":\"https://stark-architect-showcase.lovable.app\",\"subtitle\":\"Showcase your architecture work with a disciplined, minimal portfolio. Project filtering, dark mode, and integrated blog—go live in hours, not weeks.\",\"tagline\":\"Firm website \u0026 showcase\",\"description\":\"This template gives you an architecture portfolio with project galleries, category filtering, and a clean monochrome design that requires no design skills.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Architect Portfolio Website Template | Architecture Sites | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Showcase your architecture work with a clean, professional portfolio template. Optimised for architects and architecture students - launch in hours.\",\"subcategory\":\"portfolio\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/architect-portfolio-1-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/architect-portfolio-1-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/architect-portfolio-1-screenshot.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"Shipit by Brthrs\",\"avatar\":\"https://storage.googleapis.com/gpt-engineer-file-uploads/8jp6KAG7qJZgRp4lIs04ZYXqlhL2/shipitlogo.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"is_partner_template\":true,\"partner_profile_url\":\"/experts/shipit-by-brthrs\",\"date\":\"2025-12-01T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"buildings\",\"title\":\"Minimal Monochrome Design System\",\"description\":\"Disciplined neutral palette that removes visual noise so your architecture work sets the tone\"},{\"icon\":\"filter\",\"title\":\"Project Gallery with Filtering\",\"description\":\"Category-based filtering lets clients find relevant work by type—residential, commercial, cultural, or mixed-use\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Dark Mode Support Built-In\",\"description\":\"System-aware theme switching provides comfortable viewing for late-night research and client presentations\"},{\"icon\":\"newspaper\",\"title\":\"Integrated Blog Platform\",\"description\":\"Publish project case studies, design insights, and thought leadership alongside your portfolio work\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Projects display correctly on all devices with orderly navigation and friction-free browsing\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Full-Width Project Galleries\",\"description\":\"Large imagery with clear project information including location, area, year, and category helps clients evaluate your experience at a glance\"},{\"title\":\"Category-Based Project Filtering\",\"description\":\"Visitors can filter by project type to find relevant work immediately, making it easier to match your experience with their needs\"},{\"title\":\"Studio Identity Pages\",\"description\":\"Complete pages for services, process, and team help communicate your approach instead of relying solely on final images\"},{\"title\":\"Project Case Study Support\",\"description\":\"Topic filters and structured layouts let you publish detailed project walkthroughs, design thinking, and documented expertise\"},{\"title\":\"Neutral Typography System\",\"description\":\"Clean typographic hierarchy with professional font pairing creates a refined aesthetic that suits architecture and design studios\"},{\"title\":\"Contact Integration Ready\",\"description\":\"Direct contact links and Supabase form integration help qualified leads reach out without extra steps\"},{\"title\":\"Responsive Image Handling\",\"description\":\"Lazy loading and optimized delivery ensure high-quality imagery loads fast on all devices without compromising presentation\"},{\"title\":\"Dark Mode Theme System\",\"description\":\"Complete CSS variable system with light and dark themes provides comfortable viewing across different environments\"},{\"title\":\"Blog with Topic Filtering\",\"description\":\"Share updates, project walkthroughs, and design insights with organized topic filtering for easy navigation\"},{\"title\":\"Professional Navigation Structure\",\"description\":\"Orderly menu system with mobile hamburger menu ensures visitors can move through your work without confusion\"},{\"title\":\"SEO-Optimized Structure\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML, proper heading hierarchy, and meta tag configuration help potential clients discover your portfolio\"},{\"title\":\"Customizable Design Tokens\",\"description\":\"CSS custom properties for colors, spacing, and typography let you adapt the template to your studio identity\"}],\"content\":\"$4f\",\"relativePath\":\"architect-portfolio-1.md\"},{\"slug\":\"vesper\",\"id\":\"d2978eed-f6ef-4218-9f17-da78dfe6d5cc\",\"title\":\"Fashion blog\",\"pageTitle\":\"Vesper - Fashion Blog Template\",\"category\":\"Websites\",\"project_id\":\"a37d1d0d-556a-4b16-af20-d0385b80500f\",\"url\":\"https://vesper-blog.lovable.app/\",\"subtitle\":\"A sophisticated fashion blog template that combines editorial excellence with sustainable design principles.\",\"tagline\":\"Minimal, playful design\",\"description\":\"A sophisticated fashion blog template that combines editorial excellence with sustainable design principles. Perfect for fashion bloggers, style influencers, and brands committed to conscious fashion.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Fashion Blog Template | Editorial Layouts | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"An elegant fashion blog template with editorial layouts and a sustainable design focus. Built with React and Tailwind CSS - ready to publish today.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Fashion\",\"Style\",\"Design\",\"Lifestyle\",\"Sustainable\"],\"screenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/vesper-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/vesper-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/previews/vesper-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#FAFAFA\",\"#1A1A1A\",\"#F5F5F5\",\"#2C2C2C\",\"#E8E8E8\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2025-10-13T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"image_stack\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Fashion Design\",\"description\":\"High-fashion magazine aesthetic with vibrant colorful cards and dramatic typography system\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"CSS-only animations, static data architecture, and minimal JavaScript for sub-2s load times\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Layout\",\"description\":\"Adaptive grid system transforming 1 to 3 columns with immersive edge-to-edge mobile experience\"},{\"icon\":\"accessibility\",\"title\":\"Built for Accessibility\",\"description\":\"Semantic HTML, AAA contrast ratios, keyboard navigation, and screen reader optimized structure\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO-Ready Architecture\",\"description\":\"Prepared for dynamic meta tags, structured data, and social sharing optimization capabilities\"},{\"icon\":\"code\",\"title\":\"Extensible Modern Stack\",\"description\":\"React 18, TypeScript, Tailwind CSS with Lovable Cloud integration ready for scaling\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Vibrant Color System\",\"description\":\"Eight distinct card colors with warm cream background and pure black typography.\"},{\"title\":\"Premium Typography\",\"description\":\"Lora serif body text and Supreme sans-serif headings with responsive scaling.\"},{\"title\":\"Interactive Article Cards\",\"description\":\"Hover effects with grayscale-to-color transitions and consistent grid layouts.\"},{\"title\":\"Featured Content Display\",\"description\":\"Hero split layout with prominent call-to-action for editorial curation.\"},{\"title\":\"Newsletter Integration\",\"description\":\"Email capture with validation, async submission, and toast notifications.\"},{\"title\":\"Progressive Loading\",\"description\":\"Load-more pagination starting at 6 articles, maintaining scroll position.\"},{\"title\":\"Related Articles\",\"description\":\"Contextual recommendations on article pages to drive deeper engagement.\"},{\"title\":\"Dark Mode Ready\",\"description\":\"CSS variable system with inverted scheme defined, ready for one-click activation.\"},{\"title\":\"CMS Ready\",\"description\":\"Prepared for Supabase or headless CMS integration with React Query.\"},{\"title\":\"Optimized Images\",\"description\":\"CDN integration with automatic compression and layout-shift prevention.\"},{\"title\":\"Production Codebase\",\"description\":\"TypeScript strict mode, Vite with SWC, path aliases, and ESLint configured.\"},{\"title\":\"Social Sharing\",\"description\":\"Open Graph and Twitter Card meta tags with pre-configured social images.\"}],\"version\":2,\"stylePackVariants\":{\"Neutral\":\"aeaaa038-f050-4f57-b03d-7b80213d6df4\",\"Warm\":\"b788c325-6d17-4046-baa5-e9f380651e61\",\"Quirky\":\"08af2833-f2c5-48b3-b41d-b9060eee2c96\",\"Dark\":\"1137c063-3de4-48b0-9051-bb0898b8b90e\",\"Red Velvet\":\"dffa3515-3b90-4d8e-b773-e76b978f047a\"},\"designedFor\":[\"Fashion bloggers building a personal brand\",\"Style influencers creating lookbooks and outfit posts\",\"Personal stylists showcasing client work\",\"Boutique owners combining blog content with products\"],\"techStack\":[\"React\",\"TypeScript\",\"Tailwind CSS\",\"Vite\",\"TanStack Query\",\"shadcn/ui\",\"Radix UI\",\"Lucide Icons\"],\"content\":\"$50\",\"relativePath\":\"vesper.md\",\"stylePacks\":[{\"label\":\"Neutral\",\"previewColor\":\"#2c3138\",\"colors\":[\"#2c3138\",\"#E2E6EA\",\"#F2F5F7\",\"#2c3138\"],\"colorTokens\":{\"primary\":\"oklch(35% 0 0)\",\"primaryForeground\":\"oklch(97% 0 0)\",\"background\":\"oklch(98% 0 0)\",\"foreground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"secondary\":\"oklch(92% 0 0)\",\"secondaryForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"accent\":\"oklch(90% 0 0)\",\"accentForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"muted\":\"oklch(88% 0 0)\",\"mutedFor