atform with registration, maps, and real-time countdowns. Complete event management and discovery—go live in hours, not weeks.\",\"tagline\":\"Find, register, create events\",\"description\":\"This template gives you a complete event platform that looks professional and you don't need technical skills to make it work.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Event Platform Website Template | Schedule \u0026 RSVP | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"Launch an event platform website with schedule pages, RSVP forms, and speaker listings. Built for conferences, workshops, and live events - go live in hours.\",\"subcategory\":\"events\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"screenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/event-platform-1-screenshot.webp\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/event-platform-1-screenshot.webp\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/event-platform-1-screenshot.webp\",\"author\":{\"username\":\"G-W Studio\",\"avatar\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/gw-studio-logo.jpg\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"date\":\"2025-12-01T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"rocket_launch\",\"title\":\"Launch Events in Hours\",\"description\":\"Complete event platform with registration, maps, and real-time countdowns—ready immediately, no coding required\"},{\"icon\":\"image_stack\",\"title\":\"Professional Event Discovery Experience\",\"description\":\"Auto-scrolling carousels, geolocation filtering, and responsive grids that make every event look premium\"},{\"icon\":\"bolt\",\"title\":\"Real-Time Engagement Features\",\"description\":\"Live countdown timers, instant registration updates, and dynamic event status badges keep attendees engaged\"},{\"icon\":\"location_on\",\"title\":\"Google Maps Integration Built-In\",\"description\":\"Location autocomplete, embedded maps, and directions links—professional navigation without complex technical setup\"},{\"icon\":\"shield\",\"title\":\"Enterprise-Grade Security Ready\",\"description\":\"Row-level security, role-based access control, and secure authentication protect your events and user data\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"One-Click Event Creation\",\"description\":\"Drag-and-drop image upload, Google Places autocomplete, and date pickers make launching professional events effortless for non-technical users\"},{\"title\":\"Dynamic Countdown Timers\",\"description\":\"Real-time countdowns with animated transitions automatically display 'LIVE NOW' badges during events and 'Event Ended' status afterward\"},{\"title\":\"Smart Event Discovery\",\"description\":\"Geolocation-based country filtering, date range selection, and auto-hiding ended events help attendees find relevant events instantly\"},{\"title\":\"Instant Registration System\",\"description\":\"One-click register buttons with authentication, real-time attendee counts, and automatic email capture streamline event sign-ups effortlessly\"},{\"title\":\"Auto-Scrolling Event Carousel\",\"description\":\"Infinite-loop animated carousel with hover-pause interaction showcases upcoming events professionally on your homepage without manual updates\"},{\"title\":\"Full-Screen Event Pages\",\"description\":\"Hero images, embedded Google Maps, formatted descriptions, and creator profiles create immersive event experiences that convert browsers to attendees\"},{\"title\":\"Role-Based Admin Dashboard\",\"description\":\"Comprehensive event moderation, user management, and override editing capabilities let administrators maintain quality across all platform events\"},{\"title\":\"Creator Event Management\",\"description\":\"Personal dashboard showing created events with quick-access edit and delete controls empowers organizers to manage their portfolio efficiently\"},{\"title\":\"Mobile-Optimized Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Fluid layouts adapting from 320px to 1920px with touch-friendly calendars and sheet modals ensure perfect experiences on every device\"},{\"title\":\"Supabase Real-Time Backend\",\"description\":\"PostgreSQL database with auto-generated APIs, real-time subscriptions, and secure storage powers reliable event data without backend coding\"},{\"title\":\"SEO-Optimized Event Pages\",\"description\":\"Dynamic meta tags, Open Graph sharing, semantic HTML, and clean URLs make every event discoverable through search and social sharing\"},{\"title\":\"Professional Typography System\",\"description\":\"Custom font loading, semantic sizing scales, and carefully crafted spacing create readable, premium-looking event content across all screens\"}],\"version\":2,\"stylePackVariants\":{\"Neutral\":\"5a61fd9b-5ea0-4e1b-b951-82a072d58713\",\"Warm\":\"488eb85d-d251-4dbb-8a66-bfc1cfa5f489\",\"Quirky\":\"cf48cc2a-f533-4905-8a0a-79b05398ea00\",\"Dark\":\"7b01c974-4779-4944-9a0b-dcbedb6a3a34\",\"Red Velvet\":\"22263089-616e-470a-97bf-6f41af493f0e\"},\"designedFor\":[\"Event organizers running conferences and workshops\",\"Community builders hosting recurring meetups\",\"Conference teams managing registration and attendees\",\"Workshop facilitators selling tickets and enrollments\"],\"techStack\":[\"React\",\"TypeScript\",\"Tailwind CSS\",\"Vite\",\"TanStack Query\",\"Supabase\",\"Zod\",\"shadcn/ui\",\"Radix UI\",\"Lucide Icons\"],\"content\":\"$51\",\"relativePath\":\"event-platform-1.md\",\"stylePacks\":[{\"label\":\"Neutral\",\"previewColor\":\"#2c3138\",\"colors\":[\"#2c3138\",\"#E2E6EA\",\"#F2F5F7\",\"#2c3138\"],\"colorTokens\":{\"primary\":\"oklch(35% 0 0)\",\"primaryForeground\":\"oklch(97% 0 0)\",\"background\":\"oklch(98% 0 0)\",\"foreground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"secondary\":\"oklch(92% 0 0)\",\"secondaryForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"accent\":\"oklch(90% 0 0)\",\"accentForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"muted\":\"oklch(88% 0 0)\",\"mutedForeground\":\"oklch(50% 0 0)\",\"card\":\"oklch(94% 0 0)\",\"cardForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"popover\":\"oklch(94% 0 0)\",\"popoverForeground\":\"oklch(30% 0 0)\",\"destructive\":\"