esigned for wellness, travel, and personal growth content. Features elegant layouts, inspiring design, and comprehensive content organization perfect for lifestyle influencers and educators.\",\"metaTitle\":\"Lifestyle Blog Template | Wellness \u0026 Travel | Lovable\",\"metaDescription\":\"A professional lifestyle blog template covering wellness, travel, and personal growth. Built with React and Tailwind - ready to customise and publish.\",\"subcategory\":\"blog\",\"platform\":\"Web\",\"tags\":[\"Blog\",\"Lifestyle\",\"Wellness\",\"Travel\",\"Personal Growth\",\"Content\"],\"screenshot\":\"https://pub-bb2e103a32db4e198524a2e9ed8f35b4.r2.dev/a8b116a9-20b6-43a8-ae91-693ba5a35c3b/id-preview-172571d0--7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2.lovable.app-1760028648399.png\",\"thumbnail\":\"https://pub-bb2e103a32db4e198524a2e9ed8f35b4.r2.dev/a8b116a9-20b6-43a8-ae91-693ba5a35c3b/id-preview-172571d0--7410f81b-8218-4f2d-bb32-1ba1f84eabb2.lovable.app-1760028648399.png\",\"previewScreenshot\":\"https://assets.lovable.dev/templates/previews/perspective-lifestyle-preview.webp\",\"colorPalette\":[\"#F5F1E8\",\"#3D3D3D\",\"#6B7280\",\"#4A3728\",\"#FAFAFA\"],\"author\":{\"username\":\"Lovable\",\"avatar\":\"https://lovable.dev/img/logo/lovable-icon-bg-light.png\"},\"shownOn\":[\"homepage\",\"dashboard-templates\",\"templates\"],\"is_partner_template\":false,\"date\":\"2025-10-09T10:00:00.000Z\",\"highlights\":[{\"icon\":\"stars\",\"title\":\"Editorial-Grade Design System\",\"description\":\"Premium typography and warm aesthetic optimized for content-focused blogs and publications\"},{\"icon\":\"newspaper\",\"title\":\"Content-First Architecture\",\"description\":\"Multi-section articles with categories, tags, and related content for superior discoverability\"},{\"icon\":\"half_moon\",\"title\":\"Built-in Dark Mode\",\"description\":\"Complete light and dark theme system with automatic detection and preference persistence\"},{\"icon\":\"gauge\",\"title\":\"Lightning-Fast Performance\",\"description\":\"Vite-powered development with optimized builds, tree-shaking, and GPU-accelerated animations for sub-2s loads\"},{\"icon\":\"phone_iphone\",\"title\":\"Mobile-First Responsive Design\",\"description\":\"Touch-optimized interactions and adaptive layouts across all devices from phones to desktops\"},{\"icon\":\"search\",\"title\":\"SEO \u0026 Accessibility Ready\",\"description\":\"WCAG AAA contrast ratios, semantic markup, and complete meta tag structure for discoverability\"}],\"features\":[{\"title\":\"Sophisticated Typography Hierarchy\",\"description\":\"Premium Google Fonts pairing of Inter and Merriweather with fluid responsive scaling for exceptional readability across all screen sizes\"},{\"title\":\"Category-Based Content Organization\",\"description\":\"Seven semantic categories with unique color coding, dedicated landing pages, and intelligent filtering for intuitive content discovery and navigation\"},{\"title\":\"Advanced Card Hover Effects\",\"description\":\"Dual-shadow elevation system with scale transforms and image zoom effects creating engaging, modern interactions that guide user attention\"},{\"title\":\"Related Content Engine\",\"description\":\"Automatic category-based article recommendations displayed in three-column grids to increase time-on-site and reduce bounce rates significantly\"},{\"title\":\"Social Sharing Integration\",\"description\":\"Platform-optimized share buttons for Twitter, Facebook, and LinkedIn with copy-link functionality and toast notifications for seamless content distribution\"},{\"title\":\"Newsletter Subscription Forms\",\"description\":\"Multiple strategically-placed email capture CTAs with rounded-full styling, ready for Mailchimp or ConvertKit integration to grow subscriber lists\"},{\"title\":\"TypeScript Full-Stack Foundation\",\"description\":\"Type-safe React components with strict interfaces and path aliases enabling confident refactoring, easy maintenance, and seamless CMS integration\"},{\"title\":\"Customizable Design Tokens\",\"description\":\"CSS variable-based color system and spacing scale allowing instant brand customization without touching component code or complex configurations\"},{\"title\":\"Author Attribution System\",\"description\":\"Rich author profiles with avatars and bios, creating credibility and personality while supporting multiple contributors for growing editorial teams\"},{\"title\":\"Glassmorphism UI Elements\",\"description\":\"Backdrop-blur floating buttons and semi-transparent overlays adding sophisticated depth and modern polish to category badges and navigation pills\"},{\"title\":\"Staggered Entry Animations\",\"description\":\"Progressive reveal animations with customizable delays creating cinematic page loads that feel premium and guide attention through content hierarchy\"},{\"title\":\"Production-Ready Deployment\",\"description\":\"Optimized Vite build pipeline with automatic code splitting, CSS purging, and static output ready for Vercel, Netlify, or any CDN\"}],\"version\":2,\"stylePackVariants\":{\"Neutral\":\"cf130624-6a88-446e-9ac7-fc1e9cbce027\",\"Warm\":\"88794be6-170a-473f-af77-9ee4e6fa81a6\",\"Quirky\":\"0bf4d1c9-a9a0-42e7-b0e8-b3cdeff0ee6e\",\"Dark\":\"be3642ae-98c0-4fe4-b9b6-170f8a39ca53\",\"Red Velvet\":\"2cde2056-5a9e-45a9-9369-3e6665678faa\"},\"designedFor\":[\"Writers and journalists building independent publications\",\"Industry experts sharing insights and analysis\",\"Creators monetizing through subscriptions and sponsorships\",\"Thought leaders establishing authority in their field\"],\"techStack\":[\"React\",\"TypeScript\",\"Tailwind CSS\",\"Vite\",\"TanStack Query\",\"shadcn/ui\",\"Radix UI\",\"Lucide Icons\"],\"content\":\"$52\",\"relativePath\":\"perspective-lifestyle.md\",\"stylePacks\":[{\"label\":\"Neutral\",\"previewColor\":\"#2c3138\",\"colors\":[\"#2c3138\",\"#E2E6EA\",\"#F2F5F7\",\"#2c3138\"],\"colorTokens\":{\"primary\":\"oklch(35% 0 0)\",\"primaryForeground\":\"oklch(97% 0 0)\",\"bac